HEADWORD: Housebote
<hw>House"bote`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>House</ets>
+ <ets>bote</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Wood allowed to a tenant
for repairing the house and for fuel. This latter is often called
<xex>firebote</xex>. See <er>Bote</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

